Stack:
  Hotwire + Stimulus + Propshaft com esbuild (27/06/2025)

A cada alteração em css ou js, rodar:

'npm run build:css' para atualizar 'app/assets/builds/application.css'
'npm run build:js' para atualizar 'app/assets/builds/application.js'


--------------------------------

**** REMOVENDO IMPORT MAPS

remove tags from application.rb
replace: <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>

Passaremos a usar o Propshaft
<%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
gem 'propshaft', '~> 1.1'
local oficial: app/assets/javascript

bin/importmap unpin @hotwired/turbo-rails
bin/importmap unpin @hotwired/turbo-rails

Instalar Hotwire:

rails javascript:install:webpack

rails stimulus:install
